CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 23, 1945, pg. 20, reads: "Reed Kings - Two of the big reasons why Will Hitchcock's orchestra is right on top of the musical heap are Orlando Wright and Charles Pendleton.  Wright formerly played with Fletcher Henderson, Tiny Bradshaw and other top bands.  Patterson [Pendleton] is an original member of the Hitchcock crew. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Orlando Wright and Charles Pendelton or Pendleton posed with saxophones in Harris Studio
